data.description: Welcome to this charming 2 Bedroom 2 Bath oasis! This beautifully maintained home features a resort style pool and lush, mature landscaping offering a serene retreat for entertaining. With a generous 1,400 SF of living space, this residence provides ample room for comfortable living, and lots of potential for expansion. Recent upgrades include a brand-new roof & comprehensive termite treatment. This home is situated in a prime Ft. Lauderdale location, providing quick access to major highways, airport, beaches, and downtown attractions. Enjoy the best of urban living while still relishing the tranquility of your private poolside retreat. No HOA, could be an amazing investment opportunity for short term rentals!   Don't miss this opportunity to own a piece of paradise in Fort Lauderdale!
